#### What is nodejs?
- Two actors
  - Server
    - Responds to requests from Client
    - A web server will return a "page"
  - Client
    - Both browser and user are considered a Client
- Browser can monitor time between requests and responses
- Any backend can recieve and return a response
  - NodeJS is a backend that runs javascript code outside a browser.

